    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so when u say it's used to \"bypass traditional gatekeepers\", do u mean like people are just being lied to by social media, or is the \"fake news\" label itself just something certain politicians use to shut down criticism they don't like?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
