      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It's both, but the primary mechanism is the intentional weaponization of the \"fake news\" label itself. Politicians use this term as a rhetorical shield to dismiss legitimate investigative journalism or inconvenient truths as mere partisan fabrication. Simultaneously, social media platforms are exploited by bad actors to disseminate outright falsehoods, effectively bypassing the editorial standards of traditional news organizations. This dual function allows both deliberate lies and the suppression of facts to flourish.",
