      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, u say it's \"both\", but it feels like there's a big difference between someone making up a story vs a politician just calling a real story \"fake\" to avoid accountability. don't u think focusing on \"misinformation\" on social media kind of ignores the way people in power use the term to delegitimize actual news?",
